Greek Opposition Leader Rejects Papandreou Offer on EU Summit

-- B y   M a r i a   P e t r a k i s
-- 
2011-10-19T09:13:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-19/greek-opposition-leader-rejects-papandreou-offer-on-eu-summit.html
Greek Prime Minister  George Papandreou ’s invitation to main opposition party leader Antonis
Samaras to attend the European Union summit on Oct. 23 was
turned down, government spokesman Elias Mosialos said.  Papandreou’s offer was made in the spirit of showing there
is a common front in  Greece , Mosialos said in an e-mailed
statement from his office in  Athens  today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Maria Petrakis at 
 mpetrakis@bloomberg.net  